==English==
===Etymology===
Contracted from '''[[chlorine|chlor(ine)]]''' and '''[[alcohol|al(cohol)]]'''

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun-unc}}

#A [[colourless]] [[narcotic]] liquid, obtained at first by the action of chlorine on alcohol and that, when treated with water, produces [[chloral hydrate]].

